ere smallest when including synthetic measurements for arterial\npressure and valvular flow rate at approximately 2% and degraded to roughly 5%\nwhen including volume trends as well. However, the latter resulted in better\ntracking of the left ventricle pressure waveforms and may be considered when\nthe necessary equipment is available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 19:19:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-26"}
