ammatical gibberish text; and surprisingly,\nthose gibberish prompts are transferrable between different LMs to retain\nsignificant performance, indicating LM prompting may not follow human language\npatterns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 07:50:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2022 17:31:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 22 Oct 2022 15:21:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-25"}
